document_data.name: Battle of Wui Eyong
document_data.mainbody:
The '''Battle of Wui Eyong''' was battle fought in the year Koryo 812<ref group="note">The date "Koryo 812" is unknown in familiar calendar systems. between the forces of [[Koryo]] and [[Kozakura]]. 

The hero [[Niofu Sangto]], holder of the ''[[sitting dog]]'' chalice, defeated the Kozakuran navy in the battle.
